native.query:
with filtered_granularity as (
    select distinct granularity
    from MD.FATPAY_DASHBOARD_HELP_TABLE
    where {{granularity}}
          AND granularity is not null
),

filtered_groupby as (
    select distinct fatpay_columns_groupby
    from MD.FATPAY_DASHBOARD_HELP_TABLE
    where {{groupby}}
          AND fatpay_columns_groupby is not null
),

filtered_fatpay as (
    select *
    from MART.FATPAY
    where -- IS_CARD_BINDING = FALSE and IS_REPEAT = FALSE and 
        {{CREATED_AT}}
        and {{CARD_GEOSCHEME}}
        and {{CARD_COUNTRY}}
        and {{STATUS}}
        and {{BUSINESS_NAME}}
        and {{USER_NAME}}
        and {{FIAT_CURRENCY}}
        and {{ACQUIRER}}
        and {{CARD_BRAND}}
        and {{PAYMENT_TERMINAL}}
        and {{ERROR_GROUP}}
        and {{ERROR_NAME}}
        and {{HAS_ID_PROVIDER}}
        and {{SHOP}}
        and {{is_aft}}
        and day(created_at) <= {{day_number}}
),

pre_top_n as (
    select 
        CASE 
            WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Fiat Currency'
                THEN fatpay.CURRENCY
            WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Status'
                THEN fatpay.STATUS_NAME
            WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'User Name'
                THEN fatpay.USER_NAME
            WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Merchant'
                THEN fatpay.BUSINESS_NAME
            WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Shop'
                THEN fatpay.SHOP_NAME
            WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Acquirer'
                THEN fatpay.DRIVER_NAME
            WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Payment Terminal'
                THEN fatpay.PAYMENT_SYSTEM_NAME
            WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Card Bank'
                THEN fatpay.CARD_BANK
            WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Card Brand'
                THEN fatpay.CARD_BRAND
            WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Card Type'
                THEN fatpay.CARD_TYPE
            WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Card Geoscheme'
                THEN fatpay.CARD_GEOSCHEME_BUSINESS
            WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Card Country'
                THEN fatpay.CARD_BANK_ISO_COUNTRY
            WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Antifraud Status'
                THEN fatpay.ANTIFRAUD_STATUS
            WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Is AFT'
                THEN fatpay.IS_AFT
            ELSE null 
        END as grouping,
        row_number() over (order by sum(fatpay.AMOUNT_EUR) desc) as rn
    from filtered_fatpay as fatpay
    left join filtered_groupby as groupby
        on 1 = 1
    group by 1 
),

top_n as (
    select 
        grouping,
        CASE 
            WHEN rn < {{top_n}} 
                THEN grouping
        ELSE 'others' END AS grouping_top_n
    from pre_top_n
)

select 
    date_trunc(gran.granularity, fatpay.CREATED_AT) as created_at,
    top_n.grouping_top_n,
    sum(fatpay.AMOUNT_EUR) as sum_of_transactions    
from filtered_fatpay as fatpay
left join filtered_granularity as gran
    on 1 = 1
left join filtered_groupby as groupby
    on 1 = 1
left join top_n
    on top_n.grouping = CASE 
        WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Fiat Currency'
            THEN fatpay.CURRENCY
        WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Status'
            THEN fatpay.STATUS_NAME
        WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'User Name'
            THEN fatpay.USER_NAME
        WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Merchant'
            THEN fatpay.BUSINESS_NAME
        WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Shop'
            THEN fatpay.SHOP_NAME
        WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Acquirer'
            THEN fatpay.DRIVER_NAME
        WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Payment Terminal'
            THEN fatpay.PAYMENT_SYSTEM_NAME
        WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Card Bank'
            THEN fatpay.CARD_BANK
        WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Card Brand'
            THEN fatpay.CARD_BRAND
        WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Card Type'
            THEN fatpay.CARD_TYPE
        WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Card Geoscheme'
            THEN fatpay.CARD_GEOSCHEME_BUSINESS
        WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Card Country'
            THEN fatpay.CARD_BANK_ISO_COUNTRY
        WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Antifraud Status'
            THEN fatpay.ANTIFRAUD_STATUS
        WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Is AFT'
            THEN fatpay.IS_AFT
        ELSE null 
    END
group by 1, 2

        --and {{STATUS}}

        and {{USER_NAME}}

),

pre_top_n as (
    select 
        CASE 
            WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Fiat Currency'
                THEN fatpay.CURRENCY
            WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Status'
                THEN fatpay.STATUS_NAME
            WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'User Name'

            WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Card Brand'

            WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Card Type'

            WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Card Geoscheme'
                THEN fatpay.CARD_GEOSCHEME_BUSINESS
            WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Card Country'
                THEN fatpay.CARD_BANK_ISO_COUNTRY
            WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Antifraud Status'

            WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Is AFT'

    top_n.grouping_top_n as 'Grouping',
    date_trunc(gran.granularity, fatpay.CREATED_AT) as 'Created at',
    count(distinct fatpay.order_id) as 'Number of total transactions',
    count(distinct case when status_name = 'complete' then fatpay.order_id end) as 'Number of complete transactions',

    on 1 = 1

        WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Card Bank'

        WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Card Brand'

        WHEN groupby.fatpay_columns_groupby = 'Card Type'
